description: This skill will have Alexa read to you the top 5 news articles (up-voted or newest) on Hacker News, YC's computer science and entrepreneurship social news site - https://news.ycombinator.com
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Hacker News what's top
Alexa, ask Hacker News for the newest items
name: Hacker News Articles
shortDescription: Have Alexa read out the top and latest articles on Hacker News
